description: Misen Energy AB is an upstream oil and gas company with operations in Ukraine. The company is headquartered in Goeteborg, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 118 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2007-06-12. The firm is operational in Ukraine and is oriented towards the production of natural gas. During the fiscal year 2011, the Company acquired Misen Enterprises AB and its wholly owned Ukrainian subsidiary, LLC Karpatygaz. As of December 31, 2011, the Company also owned Capital Oil Resources AB, based in Swede and Capital Oil (UK) Ltd, based in the United Kingdom.
name: Misen Energy AB (publ)
